953
01:25:54,649 --> 01:25:57,861
He may be sentenced to death swiftly.

954
01:25:57,944 --> 01:26:02,240
The methods used by Ashikaga in the
Nishitokyo incident are reminiscent of…

955
01:26:02,824 --> 01:26:04,784
- I'm back.
- Hey.

956
01:26:12,333 --> 01:26:14,460
- Hey, Yomota…
- Yes?

957
01:26:15,044 --> 01:26:16,421
What were you talking about just now?

958
01:26:19,382 --> 01:26:21,384
You were talking
about security and the police…

959
01:26:25,638 --> 01:26:27,307
Don't worry about it.

960
01:26:27,390 --> 01:26:29,851
Make sure you take good care of Yoshiko.

961
01:26:35,565 --> 01:26:39,110
Hello. Care Home Aoba.

962
01:26:41,988 --> 01:26:44,532
Yes, she is here today.

963
01:26:44,616 --> 01:26:48,494
Please wait a moment.
Mai, it's your mother.

964
01:26:54,584 --> 01:26:55,793
Hello.

965
01:26:57,128 --> 01:26:58,213
Huh?

966
01:26:58,296 --> 01:27:00,298
AN UNEMPLOYED MAN HAS BEEN ARRESTED
ON SUSPICION

967
01:27:00,381 --> 01:27:02,217
OF MURDERING A FAMILY IN NISHITOKYO

968
01:27:06,095 --> 01:27:07,180
Hello?

969
01:27:07,263 --> 01:27:10,516
It's Nasu! They've found Nasu!

970
01:27:10,600 --> 01:27:11,517
What?

971
01:27:11,601 --> 01:27:13,269
I'm going to send you a link.

972
01:27:13,853 --> 01:27:14,979
Here you go.

973
01:27:17,649 --> 01:27:19,192
MISSED CALL FROM MOM

974
01:27:19,275 --> 01:27:20,735
MESSAGE

975
01:27:24,072 --> 01:27:26,199
DOESN'T HE LOOK LIKE KABURAGI?

976
01:27:27,951 --> 01:27:30,161
DOESN'T HE LOOK LIKE KABURAGI?

977
01:27:37,669 --> 01:27:39,587
Roger. We'll be there as soon as we can.

978
01:27:40,213 --> 01:27:44,300
We have the location. He's
at Care Home Aoba in Suwa City, Nagano.

979
01:27:44,384 --> 01:27:47,428
It seems like the surviving family member,
Yoshiko Io, resides there.

980
01:27:48,263 --> 01:27:49,305
Oh…

981
01:27:49,973 --> 01:27:51,516
The prefectural police
are already on their way.

982
01:28:05,571 --> 01:28:06,572
Yoshiko,

983
01:28:07,865 --> 01:28:08,866
have you remembered what happened?

984
01:28:12,287 --> 01:28:16,582
Please, I'm begging you, Yoshiko.
I've run out of time.

985
01:28:18,710 --> 01:28:20,670
I can't remember.

986
01:28:23,047 --> 01:28:27,093
Please. Try to remember
what happened that day.

987
01:28:31,222 --> 01:28:33,933
Yoshiko, I know you can remember.

988
01:28:34,017 --> 01:28:36,519
Please. Please.

989
01:28:58,166 --> 01:28:59,500
Sakurai…

990
01:29:16,934 --> 01:29:19,479
- This is Yomota, a staff member here.
- Hello.

991
01:29:19,562 --> 01:29:21,939
The escapee is on the second floor.

992
01:29:27,695 --> 01:29:29,155
Sakai,

993
01:29:31,032 --> 01:29:33,368
I have something I need you to do for me.

994
01:29:37,080 --> 01:29:39,374
I think it has been about two months.

995
01:29:42,043 --> 01:29:44,128
- You said it would be okay!
- Calm down.

996
01:29:44,212 --> 01:29:45,463
Where is my sister?

997
01:29:45,546 --> 01:29:46,672
- How could you let this--
- Kaburagi…

998
01:29:56,390 --> 01:29:57,391
Kaburagi,

999
01:29:59,185 --> 01:30:01,145
there is no use trying to resist.

1000
01:30:02,396 --> 01:30:03,898
Give yourself up.

1001
01:30:06,484 --> 01:30:08,236
I know you know the truth.

1002
01:30:09,612 --> 01:30:11,155
What are you talking about?

1003
01:30:15,409 --> 01:30:17,703
You know who the real criminal is.

1004
01:30:31,425 --> 01:30:32,677
The escaped convict in the case

1005
01:30:32,760 --> 01:30:35,096
of the Higashimurayama murders,
Keiichi Kaburagi,

1006
01:30:35,179 --> 01:30:38,224
has currently taken a hostage
at Care Home Aoba

1007
01:30:38,307 --> 01:30:41,936
in Suwa City, Nagano Prefecture.

1008
01:30:46,941 --> 01:30:50,194
We can now go live
to the elderly care facility

1009
01:30:50,278 --> 01:30:54,073
in Nagano, where Keiichi Kaburagi
is currently holed up.

1010
01:30:58,369 --> 01:31:03,040
We are about 12km from Shimosuwa Station
in Suwa City, Nagano.

1011
01:31:03,791 --> 01:31:07,211
The police have taken over the area.

1012
01:31:07,295 --> 01:31:08,754
A man who seems to resemble

1013
01:31:08,838 --> 01:31:11,924
death row convict Keiichi Kaburagi
is holed up inside

1014
